From 40a43f9be12e3632e406ea9868dfa8c97e2ea7fa Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vincenzo Grimaldi <vincenzo@igrimaldi.engineering>
Date: Mon, 6 Jul 2026 14:32:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(arm-library): sliding conveyor, aligned pick/drop,
 offset pallet, safety cell

Full clean rewrite of ProfiledArm on top of the merged floor/no-vanish work:
- Conveyor cartons slide continuously toward the pick point (per-frame refs),
  one arriving each cycle, instead of jumping between slots.
- Pick/drop aligned to the belt: a carton sits at the pick point, hands off to
  the gripper, and lands at the optimizer's exact target.
- Realistic layout: arm base at a pallet corner, pallet offset in +X (beside
  the arm, not underneath), conveyor on the -X side, wider camera framing.
- Safety fence perimeter + andon light (green building / blue done).
- Remove the two stale delivery .patch files from the repo root.

Typecheck clean; parity PASS; no engine change.
